---
// GTM Solution Section - The Answer (Daytona-style)
// Clear, confident positioning with visual proof
---

<section class="solution">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The Solution</div>
    <h2>Caro Checks Every Command Before You Run It</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Natural language in. Safe, platform-specific commands out. 52+ dangerous patterns blocked automatically.
    </p>

    <div class="solution-visual">
      <div class="flow-diagram">
        <!-- Input -->
        <div class="flow-step input">
          <div class="step-label">You type</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <code>"delete old log files"</code>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

        <!-- Processing -->
        <div class="flow-step process">
          <div class="step-label">Caro processes</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="process-item">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span> Local LLM inference
            </div>
            <div class="process-item">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span> Platform detection
            </div>
            <div class="process-item">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span> Safety validation
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

        <!-- Output -->
        <div class="flow-step output">
          <div class="step-label">You get</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <code class="safe">find /var/log -name "*.log" -mtime +30 -delete</code>
            <div class="output-badge safe-badge">‚úì Safe to run</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
        <h3>Pre-Execution Validation</h3>
        <p>Every command passes through 52+ safety patterns before you see it. Fork bombs, recursive deletes, privilege escalation‚Äîall caught.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">üîí</div>
        <h3>100% Local Processing</h3>
        <p>Your commands, server names, and file paths never leave your machine. Zero telemetry. Zero cloud APIs. Complete privacy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">üåç</div>
        <h3>Platform-Aware Generation</h3>
        <p>Detects your OS, architecture, and shell. Generates commands that work on your Mac, your Linux server, or your BSD box. First time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution {
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #22c55e;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .solution-visual {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .flow-diagram {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    min-width: 220px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-content code {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: #1a1a2e;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #9cdcfe;
  }

  .step-content code.safe {
    color: #22c55e;
  }

  .flow-step.process .step-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .process-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .process-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .process-item .check {
    color: #22c55e;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .output-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .safe-badge {
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
    color: #22c55e;
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .pillar {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .flow-diagram {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .flow-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .flow-step {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .solution-visual {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
